OL,6,F"But from our prospective, as
OL,7,Fprofessionals in maritime, we wanted
OL,8,Fto change that story and actually they
OL,9,Fweren't, they were innocent they were
OL,10,Fjust going about their jobs, so we
OL,11,Ffelt we had a really important role in
OL,12,Fthat."
OL,14,FMr Jones also champions mental health
OL,15,Fand created the Seafarers Happiness
OL,16,FIndex in 2015, which monitors the mood
OL,17,Fof maritime workers.
OL,19,FThis helps shipping companies and
OL,20,Forganisations to provide targeted
OL,21,Fsupport.
