OL,4,Cimprisoned guards receives medal
OL,6,FMr Jones said: "I'm thrilled to
OL,7,Freceive the Merchant Navy Medal.
OL,9,F"It's absolutely vital that seafarers
OL,10,Fhave a voice, are listened to by the
OL,11,Findustry and seen by society.
OL,13,F"I'm glad I am able to shine a light
OL,14,Fon the important work that seafarers
OL,15,Fdo and I'll continue to champion them
OL,16,Fin the years to come."
