OL,4,Cimprisoned guards receives medal
OL,6,FSpeaking of his work on mental health,
OL,7,Fhe added: "It's a strange industry,
OL,8,Fbecause at some levels there are
OL,9,Ffantastic companies doing amazing
OL,10,Fthings and doing it very well.
OL,12,F"But below that level you get into a
OL,13,Fvery murky world where seafarers are
OL,14,Fused and abused, people charge money
OL,15,Ffor jobs, they're not paid their
OL,16,Fwages, they're often abandoned by
OL,17,Fowners who wipe their hands when
OL,18,Fthings go wrong."
