OL,3,CSailor who helped bring home wrongly
OL,4,Cimprisoned guards receives medal
OL,6,FSteven's dad was also in the Merchant
OL,7,FNavy, while his two great grandfathers
OL,8,Fserved with courage and distinction at
OL,9,Fsea with the Royal Navy during World
OL,10,FWar Two.
OL,12,FDonald Pinnington was awarded an OBE,
OL,13,Fand Thomas Williams died when his ship
OL,14,Fwas sunk by a U-Boat.
OL,16,FMaritime minister Mike Kane said:
OL,17,F"It's fantastic to see these nine
OL,18,Fremarkable sailors receive this very
OL,19,Fspecial award ` the highest in the
OL,20,Findustry.
