OL,3,CSailor who helped bring home wrongly
OL,4,Cimprisoned guards receives medal
OL,6,F"Their dedication, bravery and
OL,7,Ffortitude is truly inspiring and shows
OL,8,Fthe very best of UK maritime.
OL,10,F"I take pride in celebrating these
OL,11,Findividuals, as well as the many
OL,12,Fseafarers who make such a significant
OL,13,Fcontribution to our country, both here
OL,14,Fand abroad."
OL,16,FThe nine recipients will receive their
OL,17,Fmedals on 5 November in a ceremony
OL,18,Fwith the Princess Royal.
